title: Pirateville - Hidden Object - Requested [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
Sail the seas of fun in this spirited, hidden-object challenge 

featuring a daring pirate, a mysterious box, and a cursed ghost! Famed 

pirate, Sharpshooter Jack, has just arrived in Pirateville&#039;s bustling 

bay. Join Jack as he explores this tropical paradise that&#039;s teeming 

with eye-popping fun. Search each detailed destination and discover a 

huge variety of cleverly hidden objects and captivating characters. 

From the creators of Mysteryville, Pirateville is a swash-buckling 

adventure featuring loads of challenging levels, gorgeous full-screen 

graphics, and surprises around every corner.
    *  161 Eye-Popping Levels
    * Thrilling Storyline
    * Gorgeous Full-Screen Graphics
    * Seek and Find Fun

- Windows 2000/XP
- 500MHz or faster Processor
- 64MB RAM
- DirectX 8.1 or better
